{"id": 57850, "date": "2025-07-30T04:00:15", "date_gmt": "2025-07-30T11:00:15", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=57850"}, "modified": "2026-03-12T12:32:46", "modified_gmt": "2026-03-12T19:32:46", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-july-30-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/30/kingdom-of-days-july-30-2/", "title": {"rendered": "July 30"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1974:</strong> Bruce and the E Street Band co-headline with Roger McGuinn at The Troubadour in West Hollywood, a surprise gig that only became public three days prior. (Bruce doesn&#8217;t actually take the stage until almost 2am, however, so this technically qualifies as an entry for July 31.)</p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce wraps up a three-night stand at the Carter Barron Amphitheater in Washington DC&#8217;s Rock Creek Park, where he debuts his cover of The Drifters&#8217; &#8220;Up on the Roof.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eYu78f4lNvs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3284\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0730/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?fit=786%2C651&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"786,651\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0730\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?fit=300%2C248&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?fit=758%2C628&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3284 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?resize=758%2C628&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?w=786&amp;ssl=1 786w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?resize=300%2C248&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1975-0730.jpg?resize=768%2C636&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong><strong>\u00a0</strong>Southside Johnny guest-stars on &#8220;I Don&#8217;t Want to Go Home&#8221; when Bruce and the E Street Band bring the River Tour to Richfield, Ohio for the second of two nights.</p>\n<div id=\"v-RwhE4R38-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/RwhE4R38?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20009\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-07-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?fit=1653%2C1399&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1653,1399\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-07-30\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?fit=300%2C254&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?fit=758%2C642&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20009 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?resize=758%2C642&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"642\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?w=1653&amp;ssl=1 1653w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?resize=300%2C254&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?resize=1024%2C867&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?resize=768%2C650&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/1981-07-30.png?resize=1536%2C1300&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3288\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-0730/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?fit=800%2C882&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,882\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-0730\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?fit=272%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?fit=758%2C836&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3288 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?resize=758%2C836&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"836\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?resize=272%2C300&amp;ssl=1 272w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1981-0730.jpg?resize=768%2C847&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3289\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-0730/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?fit=445%2C643&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"445,643\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-0730\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?fit=208%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?fit=445%2C643&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3289 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?resize=445%2C643&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"445\" height=\"643\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?w=445&amp;ssl=1 445w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1984-0730.jpg?resize=208%2C300&amp;ssl=1 208w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 445px) 100vw, 445px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At the first of two nights in Detroit on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, Bruce tour premieres &#8220;Independence Day&#8221; in a new arrangement. In attendance tonight:\u00a0<em>Funky Winkerbean</em> cartoonist Tom Batiuk.</p>\n<div id=\"v-1Tbv8N9O-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/1Tbv8N9O?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dLdutnQxZUI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28507\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-30a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C1391&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1391\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-30a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?fit=300%2C163&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C412&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28507 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C412&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"412\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C163&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C557&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C417&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C835&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1113&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30a-scaled.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28508\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-07-30b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?fit=1334%2C1690&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1334,1690\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-07-30b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?fit=237%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?fit=758%2C961&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28508 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?resize=758%2C960&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?w=1334&amp;ssl=1 1334w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?resize=237%2C300&amp;ssl=1 237w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?resize=808%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 808w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?resize=768%2C973&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1984-07-30b.jpg?resize=1212%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1212w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:</strong> Bruce and the band rehearse for the final leg of the Born in the U.S.A. Tour at the former home of Big Man&#8217;s West in Red Bank.</p>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Jah Love at Key Largo in Belmar, New Jersey, playing reggae versions of &#8220;Born in the U.S.A.&#8221; and &#8220;My Hometown,&#8221; along with covers of &#8220;One Love&#8221; and &#8220;People Get Ready.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-r1cTI473-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/r1cTI473?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xVV5FTnI4FM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>The Tunnel of Love Tour nears its end with this final German show in Bremen, where &#8220;Working on the Highway&#8221; makes its tour debut.</p>\n<div id=\"v-mpsQeIHo-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/mpsQeIHo?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>At Night Five of eleven at World Tour 1992&#8217;s opening stand in the Meadowlands, Bruce performs &#8220;All the Way Home&#8221; for the first time, and &#8220;4th of July, Asbury Park (Sandy)&#8221; comes out as well, accompanied by only Bruce and Roy.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_FhpvZT3dks?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Finally! After 18 years, Bruce releases a new E Street Band album.\u00a0<em>The Rising</em> is an instant success, the darling of\u00a0 music reviewers and critics, and the catalyst for a new era that lasts to this day, cementing the return of the E Street Band. To celebrate the occasion, Bruce and the band get up early to appear on NBC&#8217;s\u00a0<em>Today Show</em> for a mini-concert. Katie Couric interviews virtually the entire band (poor Garry!) before the show. Watch that fun interview below, followed by the songs performed that morning.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ar-qvX1F0t4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-Nv6q-7zj-c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OiMBq3xASts?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CBFOdcaPAI0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>That night, Bruce and the band play a public warm-up show, where &#8220;Paradise&#8221; debuts and &#8220;Cover Me&#8221; returns after a decade of absence. &#8220;Into the Fire&#8221; features a stunning introduction that features Clarence on bagpipes, but it will be gone when the tour begins in proper.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YdsNXmNw1PI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5Oh6eapJuPI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-u6r6AnpC-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/u6r6AnpC?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p>Finally, ABC&#8217;s\u00a0<em>Nightline</em> airs Bruce&#8217;s performance of &#8220;Empty Sky&#8221; recorded a few days earlier.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-pgzJ7Iyg6Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20012\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2002-07-30a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30a.png?fit=1517%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1517,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quo