m/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?fit=300%2C267&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?fit=758%2C674&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20014 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?resize=758%2C674&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"674\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?w=1980&amp;ssl=1 1980w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?resize=300%2C267&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?resize=1024%2C910&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?resize=768%2C683&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2002-07-30c.png?resize=1536%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>Bruce&#8217;s close friend, personal assistant, and right-hand man Terry Magovern passes away at the age of 67. Terry&#8217;s life and death will inspire Bruce to write &#8220;Terry&#8217;s Song.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20015\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2007-07-30/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?fit=2067%2C760&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2067,760\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2007-07-30\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?fit=300%2C110&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?fit=758%2C279&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20015 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=758%2C279&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?w=2067&amp;ssl=1 2067w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=300%2C110&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=1024%2C377&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=768%2C282&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=1536%2C565&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2007-07-30.png?resize=2048%2C753&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>A beautiful set list in Benidorm, Spain, on the Working on a Dream Tour, as &#8220;Janey, Don&#8217;t You Lose Heart,&#8221; &#8220;Girls in Their Summer Clothes,&#8221; and &#8220;If I Should Fall Behind&#8221; receive their tour debuts and &#8220;Be True&#8221; gets a rare outing.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mZw8n91G2nY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ye-LtocznFQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TsAkWxv8AdA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G5AgJr1q0b4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>As the Wrecking Ball Tour prepares to wrap up its European leg and return to America, <em>The New Yorker\u00a0</em>publishes an extensi